    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spin the slots to build.</strong><br><strong>As her assistant, help weave her fate.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a  deck-building roguelike   where you spin the reels to build your deck, chain items and evolve them, let her to equip them, to defeat  monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the loyal attendant to a mysterious sorceress, you will <strong>help her grow stronger</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By gathering and chaining items in slots, you can create powerful synergies, enhance her abilities, and upgrade to even stronger gear. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn gold from battles to purchase useful items in the shop, then equip her before venturing into the forest to gain an advantage.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At first, you might struggle and fall quickly, unable to progress far. <br>But depending on your strategy and the enhancements from collected special items, you’ll gradually push deeper into the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One basic strategy is to<strong><u> strengthen her defensive gear while enemies are still weak.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, as the stages progress, finding your own strategy becomes key, and you will discover an addictive cycle of challenge as you advance through the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your strategy and luck will decide her fate—lead her to victory and break the curse that binds her!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134570/extras/d96bdc8ae2e7dd8cb5a0a331097f352e.poster.avif?t=1769074326\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134570/extras/d96bdc8ae2e7dd8cb5a0a331097f352e.webm?t=1769074326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134570/extras/d96bdc8ae2e7dd8cb5a0a331097f352e.mp4?t=1769074326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
